      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.sobLlAGQkmWcFBFx]{Magic Hack}</p>\n<p>Twice per day as a standard action, you can unleash a burst of raw magic in a 30-foot radius around you, dealing 10d6 damage to every creature in the area (Reflex half). Each time you use power sphere, you decide if it deals electricity, fire, or sonic damage. You can expend a technomancer spell slot when using this ability to exclude a number of squares from the area of power sphere equal to no more than the level of the spell slot expended.</p>"
